// BP_CoopBridge — Blueprint subclass of ACoopBridgeActor
// Location: /Game/Game/Blueprints/Actors/BP_CoopBridge

/*
To create in UE5 Editor:
1. Create new Blueprint extending ACoopBridgeActor
2. Set default properties:
   - RequiredActivationCount = 6
   - MonitoredShardIDs = [Shard_01_Light, Shard_02_Light, Shard_03_Light,
                          Shard_01_Shadow, Shard_02_Shadow, Shard_03_Shadow]
   - ActivationDelay = 1.5
   - LockedMaterial = M_Bridge_Locked
   - PartiallyActiveMaterial = M_Bridge_Locked (or partial glow variant)
   - FullyActiveMaterial = M_Bridge_Active
   - LowerSound = S_Bridge_Lower_Cue
   - RaiseSound = S_Bridge_Raise_Cue
   - ActivationTickSound = S_Shard_Tick_Cue
3. Place 1x instance in PrototypeRoom at (0, 900, 0)
   Bridge spans gap between Hall B and Exit Platform
4. Connect Shard IDs in Level Blueprint or via component tags
*/
